sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Web/Mobile Client
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant AM as Asset Management
    participant Kafka as Kafka Bus
    participant IG as Integration Gateway
    participant CP as Capital Planning
    participant RA as Reporting & Analytics
    participant SAP as SAP ERP

    Client->>GW: POST /api/v1/assets (JWT)
    GW->>GW: Validate JWT, check RBAC
    GW->>AM: Forward request
    AM->>AM: Validate & persist asset
    AM->>Kafka: Publish AssetCreated event
    AM-->>GW: 201 Created {assetId}
    GW-->>Client: 201 Created {assetId}

    Kafka-->>IG: Consume AssetCreated
    IG->>IG: Map to SAP canonical model
    IG->>SAP: Create equipment record (EQUI)
    SAP-->>IG: 200 OK {sapId}
    IG->>AM: PATCH /assets/{id}/external-ids {sap: sapId}

    Kafka-->>CP: Consume AssetCreated
    CP->>CP: Register asset for CapEx tracking

    Kafka-->>RA: Consume AssetCreated
    RA->>RA: Update asset count KPI
    RA->>RA: Write audit log entry
